<br>
Target a pet and practice begging. You will not get any money from the pet, but you can raise your skill. This works well while you are meditating. You just have to click on the beg icon, you cannot hit a hot key (1-6) while meditating.<br>
<br>
Target a pet and practice pickpocket. If you are a rogue this is a great way to increase skill.<br>
<br>
Target a pet and practice spells. My enchanter pets are always mesmerized by my presence. Some spells also improve if you target a corpse and fire away. <p><P><B><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Reog</FONT></B> the educated ogre of <A HREF="http://www.midnight_council.homestead.com"><IMG SRC = "http://www.midnight_council.homestead.com/files/mcsmall.gif" WIDTH=195 HEIGHT=32  BORDER=0></A></P>
<P><B><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Arlo</FONT></B>/<B><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Tinkerdo</FONT></B>
      - You spawn it, we kill it.</P>
    
